{"tid":1346521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民進黨 : 譴責港府放任暴力 黑道成為中共代理","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T04:44:04.000Z","uid":11526,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"84bc07de3115645459835ccacf343e7935d905eb","tid":1346521,"uid":11526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:20:49.000Z","msg":"港府放任白衣黑道無差別攻擊港民，面對謹守工作崗位的記者，以及身懷六甲的孕婦，仍以拳腳棍棒相待，失控情況令人詫異。黑道成為迫害港民的中共代理人，從「一國兩制」轉為「警黑共治」的香港，我們看到中共如何透過一國兩制的糖衣來侵蝕民主自由。<br />\n <br />\n在此，民主進步黨除譴責港府放任暴力，同時也將持續努力守護台灣民主。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z9dofgu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ9dofgu.png&h=b5c07820&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c4f307ec4d132e0ee8dda5f4cc5ea2a1f04e36c","tid":1346521,"uid":11526,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:35:25.000Z","msg":"台灣人要睇清楚一國兩制<br />\n你接受一國兩制<br />\n下場就會好似香港咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317dcdf656d1b7fe58a70cac641abd4fbaff4ffe","tid":1346521,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:36:20.000Z","msg":"ENGLISH再一次多謝共產黨助攻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d37ecf07cc352391ddda44eb8c9615ed483d97","tid":1346521,"uid":238370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:43:45.000Z","msg":"台灣奶共嗰個竹聯幫都唔會衝入捷運站見人就打，連大肚婆都恰下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11baa245ebb827a22b75fa0663d438386a14d8b1","tid":1346521,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:44:04.000Z","msg":"中共黑社會化！白衣人毆港民 王丹：還現代政黨咧根本大堂口<br />\n<br />\n2019-07-22<br />\n<br />\n王丹在文中指出，現在香港發生的事情，並非北京特別制定對策，「『用黑社會治理國家』，這本身一直就是中共的既定方針」，並稱「專制政權勾結黑社會」歷史上常見，「在台灣就發生過」。。。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2859974\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fm.ltn.co